Installing required software on RedHat4 (or other linux distributions which
does not have the required software for running SGAS).

Thanks to Olli Tourunen for providing this.


* Python 2.6

wget http://www.python.org/ftp/python/2.6.2/Python-2.6.2.tar.bz2
tar xvfj Python-2.6.2.tar.bz2
cd Python-2.6.2
./configure --prefix=/opt/python262
make -j 4
make install

* Zope Interface (required for Twisted)

wget http://www.zope.org/Products/ZopeInterface/3.3.0/zope.interface-3.3.0.tar.gz
tar xvfz zope.interface-3.3.0.tar.gz
cd zope.interface-3.3.0
/opt/python262/bin/python setup.py install

* Twisted Core

wget http://tmrc.mit.edu/mirror/twisted/Core/8.2/TwistedCore-8.2.0.tar.bz2
tar xvfj TwistedCore-8.2.0.tar.bz2
cd TwistedCore-8.2.0
/opt/python262/bin/python setup.py install

* Twisted Web

wget http://tmrc.mit.edu/mirror/twisted/Web/8.2/TwistedWeb-8.2.0.tar.bz2
tar xvfj TwistedWeb-8.2.0.tar.bz2
cd TwistedWeb-8.2.0
/opt/python262/bin/python setup.py install

* pyOpenSSL

wget http://sourceforge.net/projects/pyopenssl/files/pyopenssl/0.9/pyOpenSSL-0.9.tar.gz/download
tar xvfz pyOpenSSL-0.9.tar.gz
cd pyOpenSSL-0.9
/opt/python262/bin/python setup.py install

